 Till March 22 at Gaganendra Pradarsasala; 2 pm - 8 pm: Paintings by Dr Debasis Bhattacharya. 

 Till March 27 at Academy of Fine Arts; 3 pm - 8 pm: Exhibition of Beena Pradhan?s recent paintings. 

 Till March 27 at Academy of Fine Arts, North Gallery; 3 pm - 8 pm: Exhibition of recent paintings, collages and sculptures by Narayan Sinha. 

 Till April 3 (except Mondays) at Anant Art Gallery, 18A Alipore Road; 11 am - 7 pm: Colour Fields ? an exhibition of paintings by John Tun Sein. 

 March 22 - 27 (except March 25) at Birla Academy of Art amp; Culture; 4 pm - 8 pm: Chitri-O-Bhaskar Gosthi presents an exhibition of paintings and sculptures. Participating artists include Ashim Basu, Prithwis Sen, Ratan Banerjee, Chandrasekhar Acharya, Ramaprosad Ghatak, Subuddha Ghosh, Dinesh Gain, Goutam Sarma, Jiten Roy and Goutam Bhowmick. 

 March 22 - 30 at Gandhara Art Gallery, Palm Spring, Flat 5A, 1B Gurusaday Road; 4 pm - 8 pm: Recent landscape paintings by Samindranath Majumdar. 

