 March 23 at Max Mueller Bhavan; 6.30 pm: Goethe-Institut, Max Mueller Bhavan, Calcutta presents the screening of short films of young directors from the film and television Institute, Konrad Wolf, in Potsdam, Germany. 

 EXHIBITION

 March 23 - 30 at Artisana, 13 Chowringhee Terrace (1st floor), off Gokhale Road; 10 am - 7.30 pm: Crafts Council of West Bengal presents Kesh Shringar ? an exposition of rare hair ornaments from the collection of Veena Shroff, who will be present daily to demonstrate traditional hair styles from ancient sculptures and paintings. 

 Till March 30 at Design, 108 Raja Basanta Roy Road: Paramita Viswanathan?s annual summer exhibition of handloom prints, resist prints, Mangalgiri sarees, crepes, chiffons, silk, tassarprints and Hyderabad sarees. 

 SIT amp; DRAW ART CONTEST

